---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { personSchema } from "../lib/schema";
import { SITE } from "../lib/site";

const schema = [personSchema()];
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Operator shipping in public across sectors." schema={schema}>
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>/about</h1>
    <p class="text-fg-secondary text-sm mb-8">Operator shipping in public across sectors — AI agents, self-hosted infra, crypto tooling, ventures.</p>
    <p>
      Jordan Newell. Building and operating the systems behind ambitious ventures —
      a self-hosted fleet of AI agents, infrastructure across a dozen hosts, and a
      growing collection of software projects shipping into the world.
    </p>
    <p>
      Starting this blog at a moment of forced clarity: a critical-influx week
      where the organization's main infrastructure host went down at the worst
      possible time, no product shipped, no business flipped. Instead of treating
      that as a liability, making it the premise.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>The operator's desk.</strong> Field notes, post-mortems,
      manifestos when warranted.
    </p>
    <p>
      <em>Influences: Byrne Hobart's rigor, Justin Murphy's edge. The first is the default; the second is for claims worth stopping the room.</em>
    </p>

    <h2>Current work</h2>
    <p>
      Current focus lives at <a href="/now">/now</a>. Portfolio surface at
      <a href="/projects">/projects</a>. OSS work shipped to others' projects at
      <a href="/contributions">/contributions</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Let's build together</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>Practice.</strong> Defense and federal IT at <a href="https://richmondpark.co">Richmond Park Group</a> — CMMC, NIST 800-171, modernization for federal clients.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Ventures.</strong> Real stake, not employment. Currently <a href="/ventures">/ventures</a> — DW Trim, joining as Managing Partner.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>The rest.</strong> The agent fleet, self-hosted infra, this blog.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/jordannewell">github.com/jordannewell</a></li>
      <li><a href="mailto:hello@jordannewell.com">hello@jordannewell.com</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
